title: Unknown Path ~ Looking for Top Laner Diamond 5+
body:
Unknown Path is a new team looking to reach Challenger and possibly play competitively. We currently have a full roster (apart from top) who are experienced ranked 5's players. Unknown Path is looking for members who are open minded to improve, committed and active players.
Requirements:
- MUST be able to communicate either through Skype or teamspeak
- Diamond+
- Ranked 5's experience is a bonus
- Must be able to play most days of the week
- Positive attitude ( this is very important )

If you meet these requirements either add me~ IGN: LogicIsTheName or comment below outlining your:
In-Game Name:
Age:
Location/Timezone:
Rank:
Any previous experience in team environment:
Champ Pool (Best 4 champs in this role):
